<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als uns ewr gnade
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des
                                                edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Heydeck, und
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>swest<ex>er</ex></expan> sache
                                                  <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, ir
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>wei</expan>sung zu tun etc.,
                                                das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                                und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr gnade
                                                  <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                                  <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Heydeck niht
                                                mechtik seyn und bey uns niht ist, daz wir in
                                                  <expan>söllich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache niht zu
                                                  <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>weisen</expan> haben, und
                                                  <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr gnade, das in
                                                gut von uns zu versteen; denn wo wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lieb
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Thome
                                                  <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>. </ab>
</div>
